Package: kidlock
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Peter <peter@pm-consulting.be>
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11), python3-venv, dnsmasq, libnotify-bin, network-manager
Recommends: python3-gi, gir1.2-ayatanaappindicator3-0.1
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/peter/kidlock
Description: Linux parental control with Home Assistant integration
 Enforces screen time limits via PAM login blocking, session
 termination, and DNS filtering. Integrates with Home Assistant
 via MQTT for remote control and monitoring.
 .
 Features:
  - Block login for controlled users outside allowed hours
  - Force logout when time limit is reached
  - Track usage time per user
  - Desktop warnings before time runs out
  - System tray indicator showing remaining time
  - Add bonus time via Home Assistant
  - Pause timer via Home Assistant
